turns.ai_line: Good morning, doctor. Abeg, I need your help. Since yesterday when I chop the remaining rice wey I cook two days ago, my belle just dey do me somehow. I dey feel pain for my stomach and I dey purge well well. I even dey feel like I wan vomit. This kind wahala never happen to me before o. I just dey wonder whether na the rice cause am because na only me chop am and my area dey hot well well, food fit spoil quick.
Abeg doctor, I need something to make this pain stop. I no fit sleep at all last night. I dey fear say I don get food poisoning. Wetin you think say fit be the problem?
"Doctor, I even dey sweat, and I dey feel like say I wan vomit. I no well at all. E get any medicine wey you fit give me?"
